Sheepshead Bay (Brooklyn): The dock of the Rockaway Transportation Company at Emmons Avenue and East 21st Street. Shown too are the ferryboats "Uncle Sam," and "C. Washington Calyer." View 3 shows the entrance to the dock, No. 2016 Emmons Avenue.
